<div class="details theme-blue" data-id="2636882" data-title="ONTARIO: Don&#39;t get &#39;casual&#39; about COVID, top doc warns amid resort outbreak" data-tag="78585">
<h1 class="title details-title"><b>ONTARIO:</b> Don't get 'casual' about COVID, top doc warns amid resort outbreak</h1>
    <div class="details-intro">Dr. David Williams warned that the pandemic is not over and people across the province must continue to be vigilant</div>

        <div class="row">
            <div class="col-md-7 details-byline">
                    <time datetime="2020-08-14T10:44:00.0000000Z">Aug 14, 2020 6:44 AM</time>
                          By:     <span id="author">Canadian Press</span>


                    <div class="updated theme-colour">Updated <time datetime="2020-08-27T10:42:00.0000000Z" data-localtime="8/27/2020 6:42:00 AM">Aug 27, 2020 6:42 AM</time></div>

            </div>
            <div class="col-md-5 details-share">
